summary: One of the smallest and performance friendly ENB.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://img841.imageshack.us/img841/1535/s8yc.png[/img]
[size=4]One of the smallest and performance friendly ENB.[/size]

The "[i]I can play with ENB[/i] " !

[color=green]Recommended for low-end PC | Compatible with Climate of Tamriel, and Enhanced Lights and FX.[/color]

Features :
- No SSAO
- Small Blur
- Optional depth of field

To install this ENB, first doawnload the 0.113 binary here :[url=http://www.enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0113.htm]ENB 0.113[/url] (in the wrapped folder copy ONLY d3d9.dll into your skyrim folder).
Then extract the puchiENB.rar into your Skyrim folder.

I strongly recommend this mod to adapt your style :

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/17400/?]ENB Customizer by Dorian G[/url]

To uninstall use :

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30689/?]Enb remover[/url]

This is a work in progress, if you noticed bug (or suggestion)s, report to me.

Note: Based on 0.113 binary, because it's the most optimized and FPS saver.
author: Nikita
